A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Article 2 of Chapter 5 of Title 44 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
2 relating to conveyances, so as to prohibit certain entities from acquiring an interest in a
3 single-family dwelling; to provide for definitions; to provide for a short title; to provide for
4 an effective date and applicability; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
6 SECTION 1.
7 This Act shall be known and may be cited as the "Protect the Dream Act."
8 SECTION 2.
9 Article 2 of Chapter 5 of Title 44 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
10 conveyances, is amended by adding a new Code section to read as follows:
11 "44-5-49.
12 (a) As used in this Code section, the term:
13 (1) 'Homebuilder' means an entity engaged solely in the construction or rehabilitation of
14 single-family dwellings that does not have an affiliation with or conduct business with,
15 by, or on behalf of a prohibited business.
